reviews.text:
This is a hole in the wall place that has an extensive menu.  But most customers come here for it's chicken rice dish.

Kind of like the famous Hainan chicken in SE Asia but not quite the same.  It came with a special sauce and soup, all for $41.. good value, ok taste.

Just couple tables in the front.  No AC, just fans.  So brutally hot and humid in summer.
